#

Stuffed Bell Peppers with Black Beans and Corn

45 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

MexicanAmerican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuickComfort Food

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with a savory mix of black beans, corn, and spices, topped with melted cheese. A healthy and satisfying meal!

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4
  • black beans (canned): 1 can (15 oz)
  • corn (canned or frozen): 1 cup
  • cooked rice: 1 cup
  • cheddar cheese (shredded): 1 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
